snippet.title: Sonic The Hedgehog: Chaos Crush Gameplay
snippet.description:
I worked my ass off trying to beat the whole game, and sorry I kept losing balls. I gotta say, I had one ball left to go and if I didn't make it through, I would've failed it. Very old, but awesome flash game kinda looking like a Breakout arcade game from 1976. Enjoy!!
Links below:
http://www.dan-dare.org/FreeFun/Games/SonicChaos/SonicChaos.htm
http://www.arcadeboss.com/game-1895-19-Sonic-Chaos-Crush.html
https://www.gamesflow.com/jeux.php?id=201933
https://www.games68.com/games.php?id=201933
https://www.planete-sonic.com/IMG/swf/sonic%20game/
------------------------------
By Bandicam Screen Recorder (https://www.bandicam.com)
